org.bonitasoft.engine.profile

Interface ProfileEntry

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BaseElement, BonitaObject, NamedElement, Serializable

    public interface ProfileEntry
extends NamedElement, BaseElement
    A ProfileEntry represents a menu entry (inside the main top menu bar) in the Bonita BPM Portal. It can be a container (that contains other profile entries) or a link to a page in the portal. ProfileEntrys are ordered inside a containing profile entry or at the root level.
    Author:
    Celine Souchet, Emmanuel Duchastenier, Julien Mege
